<http://model.geneontology.org/R-HSA-449046_R-HSA-5660663>
        a       <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> , <http://identifiers.org/uniprot/P01584> ;
        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>
